Wmns DA8AWC5826
results.story: Pulling design details from retro shoes, the Diadora Wmns DA8AWC5826 sneaker blends classic style with modern design. Developed to echo the contours of a womans foot, the casual shoe is dressed in white from head-to-toe, subtly detailed with a pastel blue hue at the heel. Perforated logo accents are found at the midfoot, replacing the traditional leather panels. Sitting down below is a lightly cushioned rubber outsole.
